headline.print_headline: Melo, Knicks Snap 7-Game Skid, Top Wolves 118-106
headline.main: Melo, Knicks Snap 7-Game Skid, Top Wolves 118-106

lead_paragraph: Carmelo Anthony scored 33 points to help the New York Knicks snap a seven-game losing streak with a 118-106 victory over the Minnesota Timberwolves on Wednesday night.
